Two-Weapon Defense		TYPE:General.Fighter.ModifyAC																PREFEAT:1,Two-Weapon Fighting																																						PRESTAT:1,DEX=15								DEFINE:TwoWeaponShield|0											DESC:When wielding a double weapon or two weapons (not including natural weapons or unarmed strikes), you gain a +1 shield bonus to your AC. When you are fighting defensively or using the total defense action, this shield bonus increases to +2.																																																																																																																																																												BONUS:COMBAT|AC|TwoWeaponShield|TYPE=Shield|PREMULT:1,[PREEQUIP:1,TYPE=Double],[PREMULT:2,[PREEQUIPPRIMARY:1,TYPE=Melee],[PREEQUIPSECONDARY:1,TYPE=Melee]]																																BONUS:VAR|TwoWeaponShield|1																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.102
